<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Cloud Pricing API</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png" href="/img/favicon.png"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css" />
    <script>
      window.__CLOUD_PRICING_API_VERSION__ = '<%= version %>';
    </script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <img id="logo" src="/img/logo.svg" alt="Infracost logo" />
    <p id="success-message"><a href="https://github.com/infracost/cloud-pricing-api" target="_blank">Cloud Pricing API (v<%= version %>)</a> has been successfully installed! ðŸ¥³ðŸŽ‰</p>

    <div id="version-message"></div>

    <div id="configure">
      <span>To configure the <a href="https://github.com/infracost/infracost" target="_blank">Infracost CLI</a> to use this API run the following commands:</span>
      <pre>infracost configure set pricing_api_endpoint <span id="cloud-pricing-api-endpoint">http://cloud-pricing-api</span>
infracost configure set api_key SELF_HOSTED_INFRACOST_API_KEY</pre>
    </div>

    <div id="stats">
      <p>To see statistics enter your self-hosted API key below:</p>
      <input id="api-key-input" name="api_key" type="password" placeholder="Self-hosted API key" />
      <button id="api-key-submit">Show stats</button>
      <div id="stats-results"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta">
      <p>Interested in working with us to build a more data rich dashboard, or have any feedback? Email <a href="mailto:hassan.hosseini@infracost.io">hassan.hosseini@infracost.io</a></p>
    </div>
  </body>
  <script src="/js/stats.js"></script>
</html>
